---
title: Smart Mushroom and Plant-Based Ground Protein Stew with Potatoes and Spinach
description: This hearty dinner has all the flavours of a traditional stew, but lightened up. Plant-based ground protein, potatoes, thyme, mushrooms and spinach are featured in this dish that's sure to warm you up from the inside out.

